                    img.svg-house(src='/img/img/house-search-1.svg' alt='img svg')
                .buying-content-top-right
                    p.heading-sub BUYING AGENT
                    p.heading-1 Negotiating the best deal on your behalf
                    p.text-plain.

                        We will help you find, evaluate and negotiate a great deal on your new home. On average, we negotiate £25,000 off the asking price.

                    a(href)
