                    p.heading-1 A dedicated agent to manage your chain
                    p.text-plain.

                        Your dedicated chain manager will organise solicitors, other agents and everyone else in the chain to keep your move on track.

                    a(href)
                        button.btn-more More about our agents
            .buying-content-top
                .buying-content-top-left(style='order: 1')
                    img.svg-house(src='/img/img/moving2.svg' alt='img svg')
                .buying-content-top-right(style='order: 1')
                    p.heading-sub NEXERTY'S SECRET WEAPON
                    p.heading-1 Move home before you sell
                    p.text-plain.

                        If your chain starts slowing you down, Nexerty can provide a cash advance so you can move home without the hassle of chain. Terms and additional fees apply.

                    a(href)
                        button.btn-more.

                            More about moving chain-free

            .find-out
                .find-out-left
                    p.heading-sub FIND OUT MORE
                    p.text-plain.

                        What happens when you sell your home with Nexerty.

                .find-out-btn
                    a(href='how-it-works')
                        button.btn-more How it works

